# --------------------------------
# Security & Canonicalization
# --------------------------------

# Force HTTPS
http://*    https://:splat 301!

# Force www (canonical domain)
https://absolutesport.org/*    https://www.absolutesport.org/:splat 301!

# --------------------------------
# Nuxt 4 SSR App Routing
# --------------------------------
# Forward all requests to the Nitro serverless function
/*    /.netlify/functions/server   200

# --------------------------------
# Error Pages
# --------------------------------

# Custom 404 Page
/404    /404.html   404

# Optional 500 Page
/500    /500.html   500

# --------------------------------
# Future Abuse / Spam Mitigation
# --------------------------------
# Uncomment when /contact page is live.
# /contact    /too-many-requests.html   200!
